                               Navigation in PCP Web

   Navigation Aids

      The following tools will help you to quickly find your way around the
      more than thousand pages of Principia Cybernetica Web:

      Recent Changes
             "What's new" on this server

      Searchable index
             keyword search of all documents (titles and full-text).

      Table of Contents
             a long hierarchical outline, which provides a "standard
             ordering" through the main material.

      Random Link
             jump to an arbitrary node. Useful to get unusual suggestions for
             areas to explore.

      "Hit Parade"
             a list of nodes ordered according to usage frequency

      Map
             the picture below is a clickable map of the most important nodes
             of the PCP hierarchy.

      [ISMAP:PCPmap2.gif]
